<span id="freeTextContainer2911073354791171637">I was totally into this book, even though the ebook version was a pain in the tush to navigate. But the characters were great, I loved the storyline, etc. But what made the story go from 5 star to 3 star for me was the ending. There wasn&apos;t a satisfying wrap up, and in a romance novel, that is a mega-must. I was certain my Nook must have cut off the end, so I went out to my computer and pulled up the file that way too. But no, it was what it was. The rest of the book was awesome though.</span>
