    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer506674662" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12669541472691184893">First of all, I think the cover is really mis leading for this book. Yes, it is a little bit of a &quot;thriller&quot; but I would say it was more of a love story then thriller. Overall, I really did think it was a good book. I read it in a day, which can usually tell you if I liked a book or not. However, that being said, I felt as though too much happened in the 220 pages, and that the story should of focused more on one story rather then having 5 different stories being meshed together. </span>
  <span id="freeText12669541472691184893" style="display:none">First of all, I think the cover is really mis leading for this book. Yes, it is a little bit of a "thriller" but I would say it was more of a love story then thriller. Overall, I really did think it was a good book. I read it in a day, which can usually tell you if I liked a book or not. However, that being said, I felt as though too much happened in the 220 pages, and that the story should of focused more on one story rather then having 5 different stories being meshed together. </span>
